Task 1 – Digital Literacy Awareness Infographic

In this task, I created a one-page infographic to spread awareness about digital literacy among students. The aim was to explain what digital literacy is and why it is important in today’s digital world. I used an online design tool to present key topics such as safe internet practices, useful digital tools, and maintaining a professional online presence in a visually appealing and easy-to-understand format. This task helped me understand how to communicate important information effectively through visuals and improved my creativity and design skills.
